{"tid":1616532,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"持刀男子闖入警察總局 四名警察被斬死 疑犯被擊斃","createTime":"2019-10-03T12:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T13:00:59.000Z","uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b671b04c2de5ac55939d97a2393cb8b1d8f5d1b","tid":1616532,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎警察總局被一名持刀男人闖入施襲，消息說，四名警員死亡，這名男子其後被擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒報道，行兇男子是警局的員工，但未知工種。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期四下午約一時，警局事後被封鎖，多部緊急車輛停在外面，警局旁邊的一個地鐵站亦關閉。<br />\n<br />\n原定今日訪問土耳其的內政部長卡斯塔內押後行程，趕到警局視察。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484092-20191003.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484092-20191003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=c6369476\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484092-20191003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f3b386f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484092-20191003.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"02955df3e5687babfb42d3910bc25782f846b754","tid":1616532,"uid":269533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"4:1"},{"pid":"31d9513700c2b3531664c80aeada3c7bfe4fce2d","tid":1616532,"uid":289751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"點解可以4:1咁勁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}